  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Right to Habeas Corpus Act</title>
    <title type="display">Right to Habeas Corpus Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To state that nothing in the Authorization for Use of Military Force or the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2012 shall be construed to deny the availability of the writ of habeas corpus for any person who is detained in the United States pursuant to the Authorization for Use of Military Force in a court ordained or established by or under Article III of the Constitution.</title>
  </titles>
